release.name: v3.0.0-alpha
release.body:
## What's Changed
* Allow injecting a collection of services by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/363
* First pass at moving PHPUnit to tools directory by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/364
* Introduce code standard tools by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/365
* Add Justfile by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/366
* Task/upgrade phpunit 11 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/367
* Start triggering deprecations for pieces removed in 3.0 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/368
* Install logger in dev, improve emitter experiences by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/370
* Update to use nikic/php-parser 5 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/371
* Reflect supported versions properly (#372) by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/374
* Feature/bootstrap constructors by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/378
* Task/refactor out get methods by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/380
* Remove references to injecting a property in code by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/382
* Implement BootstrappingConfigurationProvider by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/384
* Implement more robust caching system by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/387
* Feature/functional api improvements by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/388
* Add version attribute to XML configuration by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/389
* Ensure decorator collections work, update changelog, deprecate cacheD by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/392
* Feature/cli runner by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/393
* Task/psalm coverage by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/394
* Introduce definition factory by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/395
* Allow profiles to be provided through CSV by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/399
* Make service delegate profile awaree by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/400
* Prioritized Profiles and ContainerFactory improvements by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/401
* Task/v3 release docs by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/402


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/compare/v2.3.0...v3.0.0-alpha
